{#
  src/reporting/templates/opt_out_email.txt.j2
  Generic opt-out / data removal request email body — Jinja2 plain-text template

  Required variables:
    broker_name   (str)  — Name of the data broker, e.g. "Spokeo"
    user_name     (str)  — Full name of the requestor, e.g. "Jane M. Smith"
    user_email    (str)  — Email address of the requestor
    user_address  (str)  — Current mailing address of the requestor (single-line)
    user_phone    (str)  — Phone number of the requestor (E.164 or formatted)
    region        (str)  — "US" | "EU" | "UK" | "global" — selects legal basis language
    legal_basis   (str)  — Override legal basis text (optional; auto-selected from region if omitted)
    date          (str)  — Submission date, e.g. "April 1, 2026"

  Optional variables:
    user_dob      (str | None) — Date of birth if needed for broker matching (YYYY-MM-DD)
    opt_out_url   (str | None) — Broker-specific opt-out URL to reference

  Notes:
    - If region is "EU" or "UK", the email references GDPR Article 17.
    - If region is "US", the email references CCPA (California Consumer Privacy Act).
    - For other regions, a generic privacy law reference is used.
    - This template produces the message body only (no headers).
      The Subject line should be set by the caller:
        Subject: Data Removal Request — {{ user_name }}

  Sample rendered output (US/CCPA):
    Dear {{ broker_name }} Privacy Team,

    I am writing to request the removal of my personal information...
#}
{% if region in ('EU', 'UK') %}
{% set legal_ref = "Article 17 of the General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR 2016/679) (Right to Erasure)" %}
{% set response_window = "30 days as required by Article 12 GDPR" %}
{% elif region == 'US' %}
{% set legal_ref = "the California Consumer Privacy Act (CCPA), Cal. Civ. Code § 1798.105, and applicable state privacy laws" %}
{% set response_window = "45 days as required by applicable privacy law" %}
{% else %}
{% set legal_ref = "applicable data protection and privacy laws in your jurisdiction" %}
{% set response_window = "30 days" %}
{% endif %}
Subject: Data Removal Request — {{ user_name }}

Dear {{ broker_name }} Privacy / Data Protection Team,

I am writing to formally request the deletion and opt-out of my personal
information from your database and all products and services operated by
{{ broker_name }}, pursuant to {{ legal_ref }}.

---

IDENTIFYING INFORMATION

To help you locate my records, my identifying details are as follows:

  Full name:    {{ user_name }}
  Email:        {{ user_email }}
  Address:      {{ user_address }}
  Phone:        {{ user_phone }}
{% if user_dob is defined and user_dob %}
  Date of birth: {{ user_dob }}
{% endif %}

---

REQUEST

I request that {{ broker_name }} immediately:

  1. Remove all personal information associated with me from your database,
     including but not limited to my name, address, phone number, email
     address, date of birth, and any other identifying information.

  2. Opt me out of all current and future data collection, sale, sharing,
     or disclosure of my personal information to any third party.

  3. Remove my information from any people-search, background-check, or
     public-records products you operate or provide data to.

  4. Confirm in writing to {{ user_email }} that the deletion has been
     completed and that you have notified any third parties to whom my
     data was disclosed.

---

LEGAL BASIS
{% if region in ('EU', 'UK') %}
I exercise my right to erasure under Article 17 of the General Data
Protection Regulation (GDPR 2016/679). The grounds for this request are:

  [x] The data is no longer necessary for the purpose for which it was
      collected or otherwise processed.
  [ ] I withdraw consent upon which processing was based.
  [ ] I object to processing under Article 21 GDPR.
  [ ] The data has been unlawfully processed.

Please note that failure to comply within the required timeframe may
result in a complaint to the relevant supervisory authority
{% if region == 'UK' %}(UK Information Commissioner's Office — ico.org.uk){% else %}(your national Data Protection Authority){% endif %}.
{% elif region == 'US' %}
Under the California Consumer Privacy Act (CCPA) and similar state privacy
laws, consumers have the right to request deletion of their personal
information. I am exercising that right with this request.

If you believe an exemption applies, please specify the legal basis in
your response. I reserve all rights to escalate this matter to the
California Privacy Protection Agency or relevant state authority if
my request is not honored.
{% else %}
I make this request pursuant to applicable data protection and privacy
laws. Please confirm the legal basis under which you hold my data, and
the steps taken to comply with this removal request.
{% endif %}

---

I expect a response confirming deletion within {{ response_window }}.

If you require any additional information to locate my records in your
system, please contact me at {{ user_email }}.
{% if opt_out_url is defined and opt_out_url %}

I note that {{ broker_name }} operates an opt-out page at:
  {{ opt_out_url }}

I am submitting this request via email in addition to any online form,
as email provides an auditable record of the request.
{% endif %}

Thank you for your prompt attention to this matter.

Sincerely,

{{ user_name }}
{{ user_email }}
{{ user_address }}
{{ user_phone }}

Date: {{ date }}

---
This request was generated and sent by TraceBurn on behalf of {{ user_name }}.
TraceBurn is a personal data removal tool. It does not represent a legal
service and this email does not constitute legal advice.
